high_descs: Turn right and walk to the right side of the couch.
Pick up the remote to the right of the box.
Walk to the table to the right of the couch.
Put the remote down on the table in front of the yellow container.
Turn around and walk to the second chair on the left.
Pick up the remote from the chair.
Turn left and walk back over to the table to the right of the chair.
Put the remote down on the table to the right of the first remote.
anns.task_desc: To move two remotes to the table.

high_descs: Turn to your right and go past the coffee table then turn right, between the couch and the coffee table, turn to your left so that you are facing the couch.
Pick up the remote, to the right of the cardboard box, on the couch.
Move closer to the round, glass end table to your right.
Place the remote in front of the yellow vase, on the round, glass, end table.
Turn to your right and go to the second black chair on your left.
Pick up the remote, on the seat of the second, black chair.
Turn to your left and go back to the round, glass, end table.
Place the remote on the end table, to the right of the other remote.
anns.task_desc: Put two remotes on the end table.

high_descs: Go to the sofa
Pick up the remote from the sofa
Go to the small table next to the sofa
Put the remote on the small table
Go to the couch with a remote on it
Pick up the remote from the couch
Go to the small table next to the sofa
Put the remote on the table
anns.task_desc: Move two remotes to a small table
